  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548010/extras/8bb08a6da069a176ba9c7be350bba046.poster.avif?t=1744644564\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548010/extras/8bb08a6da069a176ba9c7be350bba046.webm?t=1744644564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548010/extras/8bb08a6da069a176ba9c7be350bba046.mp4?t=1744644564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>\"The game is a battle between the robot faction and the toilet monster faction. Each character has different quirky attacks that create crazy, funny and dramatic battles. The match can start alone or play online with at least 2 players, up to 10 players<br>*** Outstanding features ***<br>- Characters have balanced power, balanced upgrades and resource accumulation throughout the game. There is no element of paying to buy upgrade resources, so everything is very balanced, winning or losing depends on your skills<br>- Fight online with friends<br>- Play alone or team up with 2 to 10 players together<br>- Tactical PVP<br>- Fight with characters with different powers and unique attack skills<br>- Many battle maps, lively and fun sounds<br>- There are 18 characters including main characters and leaders (Titans)\"",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548010/extras/8bb08a6da069a176ba9c7be350bba046.poster.avif?t=1744644564\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548010/extras/8bb08a6da069a176ba9c7be350bba046.webm?t=1744644564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548010/extras/8bb08a6da069a176ba9c7be350bba046.mp4?t=1744644564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>\"The game is a battle between the robot faction and the toilet monster faction. Each character has different quirky attacks that create crazy, funny and dramatic battles. The match can start alone or play online with at least 2 players, up to 10 players<br>*** Outstanding features ***<br>- Characters have balanced power, balanced upgrades and resource accumulation throughout the game. There is no element of paying to buy upgrade resources, so everything is very balanced, winning or losing depends on your skills<br>- Fight online with friends<br>- Play alone or team up with 2 to 10 players together<br>- Tactical PVP<br>- Fight with characters with different powers and unique attack skills<br>- Many battle maps, lively and fun sounds<br>- There are 18 characters including main characters and leaders (Titans)\"",
